      • DESCENDING_ORDER

        @Nonnull
public static final Comparator<Quality> DESCENDING_ORDER
        A Comparator sorts Quality objects in reverse order from their natural ordering.

        When used in a PriorityQueue, then the highest quality will be at the top of the queue.
